{
  "stem": "8916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the person came to-- and called us by name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came out, and it was truly safe for the time being.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's when-- then we had to move out of this area and move into another area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We left everything and took what we could carry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And moved into this-- in the attic, another attic in-- in another building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very many people were left, but the ghetto was so-- so much smaller.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was shrunk so much that we were still crowded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And soon after that the ghetto was completely liquidated and everyone was shipped to Plaszow, the camp that was being built next to the-- in the vicinity of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Walking, by marching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was just a couple of kilometers actually right out of town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let me tell you how this was done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they would only allow those people to leave who had jobs, who worked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So companies, like the brush makers company and the shoemakers company and the uniform makers, all lined up in different-- different sections.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were all allowed to or transported or-- or escorted out together, you know, in one group.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I lined up, of course, with my brush makers company.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother lined up with the cleaning ladies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the cleaning ladies were marched out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was watching my mother leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then soon after that the brush makers were beginning to move up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as I-- as I got close to the gate, there was a guard standing there, guards on both sides.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of them just pulled me out and said, that's OK.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You come later.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You can't come right now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Come later.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
